What are New Tea Drinks?
New Tea Drinks represent a revolutionary category in the beverage industry, combining traditional tea with modern ingredients like fruits, dairy, herbs, and functional additives. These beverages focus on delivering superior taste experiences while offering health benefits through antioxidant-rich ingredients and reduced sugar formulations. Popular varieties include fruit-infused teas, cheese tea, yogurt teas, cold brew interpretations, and CBD-infused functional blends that cater to specific wellness needs.
